'''''Adl''''' ({{lang-fa|عدل}}) is an [[Iran]]ian newspaper in [[Fars Province]]. The [[concessionaire]] of this newspaper was ''Mohammadsadegh Sharif'' known as Setoodeh and it was published in [[Shiraz]] since 1915.<ref>Rumi,Siroos; List of printed matters of Fars;2006;[[Ministry of Culture and Islamic Guidance (Iran)]]</ref>

